==================
Project TimeLapse:
==================

Slide Switch:
    -> When on start Time Lapse Bash Script (save to folder)
    -> When Off: Option to clear all images OR Compile to Video (preset)

2 Buttons:
    -> Hold Btn1 3sec for "Configuration Mode" (blink LED indicator / RGB color)
    -> Btn2 Select Mode: 30sec / 5min / 10min / 30min / 1hr 

3rd Button:
    -> Btn3 copy new video file to USB or Email?
    -> Indicate no USB with LED or success (RGB)


Components:
    -> Camera + Mount
    -> Thru-hole RGB LED
    -> 3x Push Buttons
    -> Slide Switch
    -> RasPi3
